    "By linearity, this equality extends to any a ∈ Tube S ′ and any ϕ ∈H C ′ 1 ⊗ H C ′′ 1.In fact, this equality holds for any ϕ ∈ H C because if any string-net constraint in C ′ or in C ′′ is violated, then ϕ is annihilated either by a Tube-action or by B C. We conclude thatB C t S ′ (a) = B C t op Ŝ′ (a).",
